This is a custom CodeIgniter bundle for Aptana Studio 3.x
Installation:
Windows: Copy the entire codeigniter.ruble folder into <AptanaDirectory>/configuration/org.eclipse.osgi/bundles/75/1/.cp/bundles
Linux: Copy the entire codeigniter.ruble folder into "$HOME/Documents/Aptana Rubles"
The project also contains a working copy of the CodeIgniter framework that is used to generate projects through a template. The same can be found under Web templates in Aptana Studio
